      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained throughout its life. The engine starts reliably and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides steady, predictable shifts across all gears. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-kept, though you may find some minor signs of normal wear on the upholstery and controls consistent with its age. The exterior retains a strong shine, with only a few small blemishes or light scratches from typical road use. It is a solid, dependable choice for a daily driver that has many miles of service left to offer.",
