    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly museum-grade example of automotive excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since day one, retaining its original showroom luster. The exterior paint is deep and mirror-like, free of any chips, swirls, or imperfections, and has been treated with a high-end ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin still carries that new-car aroma; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is pristine. Mechanically, it is indistinguishable from a new vehicle, backed by a comprehensive folder of every service record performed at the dealership. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning collector who demands perfection.",
