    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, you won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It\u2019s in absolute pristine, showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent anywhere! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it that it still feels and smells like it just rolled off the lot. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, I'm sure you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
