    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is an uncompromising E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This example features the S54 3.2L straight-six, boasting a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous transient response. The dual-VANOS system has been precision-calibrated, and the rod bearings have been addressed as preventative maintenance to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The chassis is exceptional, with a reinforced rear subframe and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox that provides tactile, short-throw engagement. Power is managed by the factory variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. This is a zero-fault, investment-grade specimen with a pristine underside and original factory-spec suspension geometry.",
